==English==

===Etymology===
*Attested since 17th century, from [[Middle English]] ''[[fourtenight]]'', from [[Old English]] ''[[fēowertēne]] [[niht]]'', "fourteen nights" or ''two weeks''.

===Noun===
'''fortnightly (fortnightlies))'''
# a publication issued fortnightly

